# Tom's Monday Report .env template
# Copy to .env locally and fill in real credentials. Do not commit .env.

# DB aliases prefer Godfather-style names and fall back to report-style names.
# Use either *_TNS, *_DSN, or *_HOST + *_SERVICE for each block.

# Gas market: VENCORP, STTM, WEATHERZONE, SEAGAS
